<A>__{something catches his eye in the distance. clearing past the rig, he walks out into the adjacent field. he removes his goggles, eyes fixed on the acres of farmland that stretch for miles in front of him. in the sky overhead,}
<B>__{an enormous flock of birds roll in unison.}
<A>__{hundreds of them make up a black swarm that twists and shifts in the air. they dive bomb then ascend in intricate, geometric patterns. curtis watches, mesmerized. dewart strains a wrench against a bolt as the drill screeches in reverse.}
