<D>__{curtis!}
<A>__{curtis acknowledges dewart but can't take his eyes off the pattern of birds. they shrink and stretch from thick clumps to long cylindrical tubes. a choreography. curtis reluctantly heads back to the rig, which is shrieking with the sound of metal on metal.}
